column5: Is here. Snow today and temps dropping to highs of -10 by next weekend. Hitting the lake this weekend for probably my last open water trip of the year. Here's hoping for plenty of big lakers and poikes.
I foresee lots of rum consumption in your future.
Stay safe and have a fishful outing. Don't forget the camera.
